title: Vehicle Image Classification
description: A vehicle image classification project using Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) implemented in TensorFlow and Keras to accurately classify images of different types of vehicles, such as cars, trucks, and motorcycles.

title: Song Reccommender System
description: A music recommendation system that suggests Taylor Swift's songs based on user preferences on audio features such as energy, danceability, and valence using pandas and Numpy libraries in Python.

title: Great British Bake Off Data Analysis
description: An analysis of the Great British Bake Off competition data using Python's pandas, NumPy, and Matplotlib libraries to uncover trends and insights about contestants' performances over more than 10 seasons.
